many different kinds of wraps.

1438
01:00:21,217 --> 01:00:22,218
A special…

1439
01:00:25,688 --> 01:00:28,725
It's an Arabic sauce called zhoug.

1440
01:00:28,791 --> 01:00:30,994
And a creamy perilla leave sauce,

1441
01:00:31,060 --> 01:00:32,395
along with this and that.

1442
01:00:32,462 --> 01:00:35,932
-One wrap.
-One wrap. Yes.

1443
01:00:35,999 --> 01:00:39,869
