1504
01:03:22,698 --> 01:03:25,268
-You're right.
-Garlic, perilla leaf, chili pepper…

1505
01:03:25,334 --> 01:03:28,004
-I think he'll blend that.
-Yes.

1506
01:03:28,070 --> 01:03:30,406
Ssamjang and perilla leaf.

1507
01:03:30,473 --> 01:03:32,308
