1552
01:05:16,846 --> 01:05:19,348
-I see.
-They use ricotta cheese.

1553
01:05:19,415 --> 01:05:20,683
Napoli Matfia.

1554
01:05:20,750 --> 01:05:22,685
He's adding perilla leaf juice
