1561
01:05:37,166 --> 01:05:39,068
He's putting in
a lot of work into the sauce.

1562
01:05:39,135 --> 01:05:42,972
Yes, Chef Edward is putting in
a lot of work into the sauce.

1563
01:05:43,039 --> 01:05:45,441
