1576
01:06:11,200 --> 01:06:13,536
-Tomato sauce.
-Tomato sauce.

1577
01:06:13,602 --> 01:06:15,805
-A.1. sauce.
-A.1. sauce.

1578
01:06:15,871 --> 01:06:17,406
-Cumin.
-That sounds good.

1579
01:06:17,473 --> 01:06:19,575
He's so relaxed.
