1580
01:06:19,642 --> 01:06:22,078
That's the class of the first place.

1581
01:06:22,144 --> 01:06:24,313
-He's relaxed.
-Tomato juice.

1582
01:06:24,380 --> 01:06:26,349
Tomato juice. I see.

1583
01:06:26,415 --> 01:06:28,651
-They're both composed.
-Yes.

1584
01:06:28,718 --> 01:06:30,720
Fifteen minutes are too short.

1585
01:06:30,786 --> 01:06:33,089
The first place is different.

1586
01:06:33,155 --> 01:06:35,524
That toss is his thing.

1587
01:06:36,692 --> 01:06:38,327
-Curry.
-Curry.

1588
01:06:38,394 --> 01:06:40,229
