He cooks the noodles
at 8 minutes and 47 seconds.

1603
01:07:16,565 --> 01:07:20,102
-He cooked that at the right timing.
-He did?

1604
01:07:20,870 --> 01:07:21,971
-I see.
-I see.

1605
01:07:22,038 --> 01:07:24,907
