to make the gnocchi either.

1606
01:07:24,974 --> 01:07:26,242
-No?
-No.

1607
01:07:26,308 --> 01:07:27,843
He just smashed some meatballs.

1608
01:07:27,910 --> 01:07:30,579
He'll make to make gnocchi
